        <sponsor name-id="S295">Mr. Pryor</sponsor> (for himself and <cosponsor name-id="S258">Ms. Landrieu</cosponsor>) introduced the following bill; which was read twice and referred to the <committee-name committee-id="SSEV00">Committee on Environment and Public Works</committee-name>
